def_cn: (构成形容词)表示“横贯”，“通过”，“到…的另一边”
def_en: trans- is used to form adjectives which indicate that something involves or enables travel from one side of an area to the other. For example, a transcontinental journey is a journey across a continent.
trans- is used to form words which indicate that someone or something moves from one group, thing, state, or place to another.
